articles.title: Protecting Children from Online Predators: The Hidden Dangers and How to be Safe
articles.content: While some predators operate openly on social media, others use the dark web to share illegal content. Law enforcement agencies worldwide, including the FBI and Interpol, actively investigate and dismantle these criminal networks. However, the fight against online child exploitation remains ongoing, as predators continuously adapt to new technologies.
